visualize project documentation through the file tree.

Usage: 
  $ treex
  $ treex add <path> <description>
  
    Available Commands:
    add         Add or update an entry in the current directory's .info file
    check       Validate .info files in a directory  
    show        Display annotated file tree (default command)

New .info files:
    import      Generate .info files from annotated tree structure
    init        Initialize a .info file for a directory

File-system:
    make-tree   Create file/directory structure from tree text or .info file

Help and learning:
    info-files  Show information about .info file format and usage
    help        Help about any command